The content is generated using [Middleman](https://middlemanapp.com/basics/install/)

- [frontmatter](https://middlemanapp.com/basics/frontmatter)
- ERB templating
- https://middlemanapp.com/basics/helper-methods/
- https://middlemanapp.com/basics/layouts/
- https://middlemanapp.com/basics/partials/
- https://middlemanapp.com/basics/redirects/
- https://middlemanapp.com/advanced/data-files/
- https://middlemanapp.com/advanced/sitemap/

